    },
    {
      "fact_id": "F2",
      "why_it_matters": "This fact establishes the context of XRPL amendment voting, implying that validators must weigh the necessity of the fix against the risk of network fragmentation or blocking. It supports the need for a decisive vote based on the merit of the fix."
    },
